About Event

​Want better healthcare results in 2026? Did we meet and talk about massively processing your healthcare data with LLMs and you were excited?

Welcome to Phylactery Party - a bi-annual gathering of friends where we work together to collect and process our health data, learning from each other as we go, to build better awareness of our personal health, form hypotheses on unresolved issues, and get results.
